metadata.name: Knights of Aros #MA01
metadata.description: Known for their splendid chivalry and heroic passion for defending their beloved region, the knights of Aros will not retreat when Aros Brightland requires their duty. Graduating from the prestigious Theros Academy, these brave souls are royal, courageous, and noble in fulfilling their oath as part of the Elder Monkâ€™s army. The whole land of Tunia knows how menacing it is to bout the Knights of Aros. Be it with a spear, sword, or hammer, the warriors of the brightest region are undoubtedly prepared to fight.
